title: 1X partners with EQT to roll out humanoids across its portfolio companies
description:
The companies intend to roll out up to 10,000 of 1X's humanoid robots across EQT's global portfolio of companies between 2026 and 2030.

The post 1X partners with EQT to roll out humanoids across its portfolio companies appeared first on The Robot Report.
